| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0955 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 41c69e9a-e11d-5fd4-aaf7-b9d4861244a8"
